{
  "stem": "4710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were given also similar clothes as like those prisoners were wearing-- some kind of underwear, a cap, and a jacket and trousers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the shoes-- that you left, the old shoes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a good pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were made especially for all of us-- solid, heavy boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then after-- afterwards, we are directed marching and into the camp, after the disinfection and shower.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were taken into barracks, where well, just sitting there numbed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was nothing what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had to learn the routine of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were told what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had to wake up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, they have given us dishes-- given us hot drinks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lunch time was-- was a kind of a vegetable soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the evening, we had bread with something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the day, it was really nothing much to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could walk in the camp, all over the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we knew that all the arrivals who came into the camp-- they are not staying there long.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they were-- they were distributed to various labor camps in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And always new faces-- they are coming and going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then they arrived-- then they arrived, the Jews from-- from Lodz ghetto, from Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then transports came from-- from Greece.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we realized it-- after our transport was almost the last of the Hungarian transports.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were just a few days later came from cities around Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But what we-- we realized it in Auschwitz itself that from Budapest, no transports are coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
